Class StringSelectMenuInteractionEvent

com.seailz.discordjv.events.model.interaction.InteractionEvent
com.seailz.discordjv.events.model.interaction.select.StringSelectMenuInteractionEvent
public class StringSelectMenuInteractionEvent extends InteractionEvent
Fires when a StringSelectMenu is used. This includes all the data that is sent with the event.

To implement this event, you must override the DiscordListener.onStringSelectMenuInteraction(StringSelectMenuInteractionEvent) method in your DiscordListener class and then register it in your main class with DiscordJv.registerListeners(DiscordListener...)

1.0
